OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1772877886
OL,3,CWater firm fine 'would not make up for
OL,4,Cdamage caused' by Brixham parasite
OL,6,FBrixham residents spoke outside court
OL,7,Ffollowing South West Water's guilty
OL,8,Fplea
OL,10,FPeople who fell ill after a parasite
OL,11,Fwas found in their water supply in
OL,12,FBrixham say any potential fine for
OL,13,FSouth West Water would 'not be
OL,14,Fsufficient' to make up for the damage
OL,15,Fcaused.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
