OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,439,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1772877886
OL,3,CWater firm fine 'would not make up for
OL,4,Cdamage caused' by Brixham parasite
OL,6,FThe company pleaded guilty on
OL,7,FWednesday to supplying water that was
OL,8,Funfit for human consumption following
OL,9,Fthe crisis in 2024, which left around
OL,10,F16,000 homes without water and made
OL,11,Fmore than 140 people unwell.
OL,13,F'Loss of confidence'
OL,15,FSpeaking to ITV West Country outside
OL,16,FExeter Magistrates' Court, resident
OL,17,FTanya Matthews said: "I don't think
OL,18,Fany fine would be sufficient if I'm
OL,19,Fcompletely honest.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,439,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1772877886
OL,3,CWater firm fine 'would not make up for
OL,4,Cdamage caused' by Brixham parasite
OL,6,F"Any fine that they get, I feel it
OL,7,Fwill be passed on to the customer. And
OL,8,Fas we already know, bills are getting
OL,9,Fhigher each year. So that's one of my
OL,10,Fbiggest worries."
OL,12,FSouth West Water has apologised for
OL,13,Fits handling of the crisis and says it
OL,14,Fis fully co-operating with the legal
OL,15,Fprocess.
OL,17,FResident Mandy Vanstone said: "There
OL,18,Fhas been loss of confidence - our
OL,19,Ffamily, we still don't drink tap
OL,20,Fwater. We drink bottled water all the
OL,21,Ftime."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,439,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1772877886
OL,3,CWater firm fine 'would not make up for
OL,4,Cdamage caused' by Brixham parasite
OL,6,FSouth West Water was prosecuted by the
OL,7,FDrinking Water Inspectorate and faces
OL,8,Fa fine when it is sentenced on 2 June
OL,9,Fat the same court.
OL,11,F'Life-changing health issues'
OL,13,FKris and Lisa Horswill both became
OL,14,Funwell when the parasite was
OL,15,Fdiscovered in May 2024.
OL,17,FKris said the company's guilty plea
OL,18,Fwas 'bittersweet'.
OL,20,F"It's never going to be enough," he
OL,21,Fsaid.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,439,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1772877886
OL,3,CWater firm fine 'would not make up for
OL,4,Cdamage caused' by Brixham parasite
OL,6,FIt's great that they've taken some
OL,7,Fresponsibility, but ultimately the
OL,8,Ffines are just going to be passed on
OL,9,Fto the consumer. The system is broken.
OL,10,FI think it needs re-nationalising. I
OL,11,Fthink that's the only way out of it."
OL,13,FLisa added: "It was just horrible.
OL,14,FI've been left with a lot of life
OL,15,Fchanging health issues. And my body
OL,16,Fwill never be the same."
OL,18,F'Utterly unacceptable'
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,439,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1772877886
OL,3,CWater firm fine 'would not make up for
OL,4,Cdamage caused' by Brixham parasite
OL,6,FFollowing the court hearing, Water
OL,7,FMinister Emma Hardy said:
OL,8,F"Contamination of drinking water is
OL,9,Frare - but it is utterly unacceptable.
OL,11,F"The communities affected by this
OL,12,Fabhorrent incident in Brixham deserve
OL,13,Fanswers, and today's guilty plea is a
OL,14,Fcrucial step toward accountability."
OL,16,F"I thank the DWI for their thorough
OL,17,Finvestigation and for their ongoing
OL,18,Fwork to protect public health and
OL,19,Fensure that our drinking water is
OL,20,Fsafe".
OL,26,@pD@AOUsD@AOUvD@dO]xD@AOU|D@EO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/9
