FL,439,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1772877886
OL,3,CWater firm fine 'would not make up for
OL,4,Cdamage caused' by Brixham parasite
OL,6,FA spokesman for South West Water said:
OL,7,F"We want to reiterate our full and
OL,8,Funreserved apology for the impact of
OL,9,Fthe incident in the Brixham area in
OL,10,F2024.
OL,12,F"We have co-operated fully with the
OL,13,FDrinking Water Inspectorate throughout
OL,14,Fits investigations. Today is another
OL,15,Fstage of this legal process which we
OL,16,Fwill continue to support."
OL,18,F'Awful event'
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,439,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1772877886
OL,3,CWater firm fine 'would not make up for
OL,4,Cdamage caused' by Brixham parasite
OL,6,FCaroline Voaden, whose South Devon
OL,7,Fconstituency covers the Brixham area,
OL,8,Fsaid she was glad the company had
OL,9,F"owned up to their serious failures".
OL,11,FShe said: "This time last year, the
OL,12,Fformer South West Water CEO claimed
OL,13,Fcustomers were among the company's top
OL,14,Fpriorities. Today, they have pleaded
OL,15,Fguilty to supplying water unfit for
OL,16,Fhuman consumption.
OL,26,@sD@KOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,439,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43809
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1772877886
OL,3,CWater firm fine 'would not make up for
OL,4,Cdamage caused' by Brixham parasite
OL,6,F"This admission of guilt has been a
OL,7,Flong time coming. I am glad that South
OL,8,FWest Water has owned up to their
OL,9,Fserious failures. This awful event
OL,10,Fshould never have happened.
OL,12,F"But the mismatch between rhetoric and
OL,13,Faction plagues our broken water
OL,14,Findustry. Whether it is protecting
OL,15,Fcustomers or the environment, too many
OL,16,Fwater firms say one thing, then do
OL,17,Fanother."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
